# Epic 3: Data Pre-Processing

## Story 1: Missing Value Handling

Identify and handle missing values to improve data quality and ensure consistency.

## Story 2: Outlier Detection

Detect and treat outliers using statistical techniques to reduce their impact on model performance.

## Story 3: Encoding

Convert categorical variables into numerical values using suitable encoding techniques.

## Story 4: Train-Test Split

Split the dataset into training and testing sets for model development and evaluation.

## Story 5: Feature Scaling

Apply feature scaling to normalize numerical attributes and improve machine learning model performance.